00:00:00,100 --> 00:03:22,000
The Rise of the Nut Warrior

3
00:03:49,100 --> 00:03:51,400
In a kingdom far far away

4
00:03:51,400 --> 00:03:53,600
Where all nyut-nyut lives,

5
00:03:53,600 --> 00:03:56,500
A sudden calamity strikes

6
00:03:56,500 --> 00:03:59,000
among the nyut-nyut who lives in harmony.

7
00:03:59,000 --> 00:04:02,100
A pink giant monster has emerged out of nowhere

8
00:04:02,100 --> 00:04:04,500
and created havoc everywhere.

9
00:04:04,500 --> 00:04:07,800
A lot of buildings and villages were destroyed.

10
00:04:07,800 --> 00:04:10,500
All nyut-nyut were left hopeless

11
00:04:10,500 --> 00:04:13,500
until a mysterious magical squirrel arrived

12
00:04:13,500 --> 00:04:15,800
to find a legendary weapon,

13
00:04:15,800 --> 00:04:17,500
the Nut Blade.

14
00:04:17,500 --> 00:04:20,500
The legend said that this mysterious squirrel

15
00:04:20,500 --> 00:04:25,800
will bring an end to this calamity...

16
00:04:47,800 --> 00:04:53,000
強くなれる理由を知った
I have learned the reason to be strong

17
00:04:53,000 --> 00:05:01,000
僕を連れて進め
Take me with you and move forward

18
00:05:01,148 --> 00:05:06,248
紅蓮華
Lyrics: LiSA  Music: 草野華余子
Gurenge
Lyrics: LiSA  Music: Kayoko Kusano

19
00:05:08,298 --> 00:05:12,898
泥だらけの走馬灯に酔う
Intoxicated by a mud-stained revolving lantern

20
00:05:12,898 --> 00:05:15,448
こわばる心
My heart stiffens

21
00:05:15,448 --> 00:05:19,598
震える手は掴みたいものがある
There's something my trembling hands want to grasp

22
00:05:19,598 --> 00:05:22,098
それだけさ
That's all it is

23
00:05:22,298 --> 00:05:24,798
夜の匂いに
In the scent of the night

24
00:05:22,948 --> 00:05:24,798
(I'll spend all thirty nights)

25
00:05:25,198 --> 00:05:28,348
空睨んでも
Even if I glare at the sky

26
00:05:26,098 --> 00:05:28,348
(Staring into the sky)

27
00:05:28,848 --> 00:05:33,548
変わっていけるのは自分自身だけ
The only thing I can change is myself

28
00:05:33,548 --> 00:05:36,048
それだけさ
That's all it is

29
00:05:36,548 --> 00:05:42,998
強くなれる理由を知った　僕を連れて進め
I know why I can be strong, take me with you and move forward

30
00:05:49,948 --> 00:05:52,448
どうしたって！
No matter what happens!

31
00:05:52,448 --> 00:05:54,448
消せない夢も
The dreams I can't erase

32
00:05:54,448 --> 00:05:56,848
止まれない今も
The present I can't stop

33
00:05:56,848 --> 00:06:00,948
誰かのために強くなれるなら
If I can become strong for someone's sake

34
00:06:00,948 --> 00:06:05,348
ありがとう　悲しみよ
Then thank you, sadness

35
00:06:05,348 --> 00:06:10,298
世界に打ちのめされて負ける意味を知った
Beaten down by the world, I learned the meaning of defeat

36
00:06:10,298 --> 00:06:14,498
紅蓮の華よ咲き誇れ！
Crimson lotus flower, bloom in full glory!

37
00:06:14,498 --> 00:06:16,948
運命を照らして
Illuminate our destiny

38
00:06:22,898 --> 00:06:27,498
イナビカリの雑音が耳を刺す
The noise of lightning pierces my ears

39
00:06:27,498 --> 00:06:30,198
戸惑う心
My bewildered heart

40
00:06:30,198 --> 00:06:34,348
優しいだけじゃ守れないものがある
Kindness alone isn't enough to protect what matters

41
00:06:34,348 --> 00:06:36,898
わかってるけど
I know that, but still...

42
00:06:37,248 --> 00:06:39,748
水面下で絡まる善悪
Good and evil tangled beneath the surface

43
00:06:39,748 --> 00:06:42,398
透けて見える偽善に天罰
Divine punishment for transparent hypocrisy

44
00:06:40,298 --> 00:06:42,398
(Tell me why, tell me why, tell me why, tell me why)

45
00:06:42,398 --> 00:06:44,298
I don't need you!

46
00:06:44,298 --> 00:06:46,948
逸材の花より
Rather than a flower of rare talent

47
00:06:46,948 --> 00:06:51,298
挑み続け咲いた一輪が美しい
The single bloom that persists through challenge is beautiful

48
00:06:51,498 --> 00:06:54,748
乱暴に敷き詰められた
