50
00:06:57,398 --> 00:07:01,748
本気の僕だけに現れるから
Will reveal its true form only to the serious me

51
00:07:01,748 --> 00:07:04,148
乗り越えてみせるよ
I'll show you I can overcome it

52
00:07:04,598 --> 00:07:07,098
簡単に片付けられた
Dismissed so easily

53
00:07:07,098 --> 00:07:09,548
守れなかった夢も
The dreams I couldn't protect

54
00:07:09,548 --> 00:07:13,748
紅蓮の心臓に根を生やし
Will take root in my crimson heart

55
00:07:13,748 --> 00:07:18,448
この血に宿って
And dwell within this blood

56
00:07:30,498 --> 00:07:34,598
ヒト知れずはかない
Fleeting, unknown to others

57
00:07:34,598 --> 00:07:37,148
散りゆく結末
