59
00:07:41,348 --> 00:07:43,998
悲鳴の風吹く
The wind of screams blows

60
00:07:44,398 --> 00:07:46,998
誰かの笑う影
The shadow of someone's laughter

61
00:07:46,998 --> 00:07:49,498
誰かの泣き声
The sound of someone's weeping

62
00:07:49,498 --> 00:07:56,448
誰もが幸せを願ってる
Everyone is wishing for happiness

63
00:07:57,648 --> 00:08:00,098
どうしたって！
No matter what happens!

64
00:08:00,098 --> 00:08:02,098
消せない夢も
The dreams I can't erase

65
