80
00:09:25,298 --> 00:09:27,648
Do you know where that monster is heading?

81
00:09:27,848 --> 00:09:30,248
I think it's headed to the next village.

82
00:09:30,498 --> 00:09:31,548
Don't worry.

83
00:09:31,548 --> 00:09:35,548
I shall take care of it for you so it won't destroy the other village too.

84
00:09:35,548 --> 00:09:39,398
In order to do that, I need to collect power by singing and music.

85
00:09:39,398 --> 00:09:43,648
So please, lend me your power, oh dear villager.

86
00:09:44,198 --> 00:09:45,898
Oh, I will.

